<description>
<![CDATA[
<img src="https://eandt.theiet.org/media/3837/google-logo-eu.jpg?crop=0,0.33435982799278674,0,0.1750034678873631&cropmode=percentage&width=1200&height=450&rnd=131430352870000000" /><br /><br />
