</link>
<media:content url="https://eandt.theiet.org/media/3881/guy-in-hoodie-at-laptop.jpg?center=0.70538243626062325,0.54427645788336931&mode=crop&width=800&height=600&rnd=131433022870000000" medium="image"/>
<description>
<![CDATA[
<img src="https://eandt.theiet.org/media/3881/guy-in-hoodie-at-laptop.jpg?center=0.70538243626062325,0.54427645788336931&mode=crop&width=1200&height=450&rnd=131433022870000000" /><br /><br />
